== 私人生活 ==
麥凱恩信仰[[基督教|基督教]][[美国圣公会|圣公会]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.usnews.com/usnews/news/election/mccain.htm |title=Candidate profile of John McCain |work=Election 2000 |publisher=U.S. News & World Report |accessdate=2006-08-16 |archive-date=2012-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120406191201/http://www.usnews.com/usnews/news/election/mccain.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=John McCain |work=OntheIssues.org |url=http://www.ontheissues.org/Senate/John_McCain.htm |accessdate=2006-08-16 |archive-date=2021-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210427171952/https://www.ontheissues.org/Senate/John_McCain.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

1965年7月3日，28岁的麥凱恩与他的第一任妻子Carol Shepp结婚，<ref name="dmr-mccain">[https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20080625184356/http://www.desmoinesregister.com/apps/pbcs.dll/section?Category=caucus&template=detail&candidate=mccain "John McCain"], ''Iowa Caucuses '08'', ''[[The_Des_Moines_Register|The Des Moines Register]]''. Retrieved November 8, 2007.</ref>并收养了她与前夫的两个儿子Douglas(Doug)和Andrew(Andy)，<ref name="feinberg" /><ref name="alexander-92">Alexander, ''Man of the People'', p. 92</ref>并育有一个女儿Sidney。<ref>Alexander, ''Man of the People'', p. 33</ref><ref name="nyt122707">Steinhauer, Jennifer. [https://www.nytimes.com/2007/12/27/us/politics/27mccainkids.html "Bridging 4 Decades, a Large, Close-Knit Brood"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2007/12/27/us/politics/27mccainkids.html |date=20180829223159 }}, ''[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]'' (December 27, 2007). Retrieved December 27, 2007.</ref> 两人于1980年2月离婚。

麥凱恩與他的第二任妻子辛蒂·亨絲莉·麥凱恩結婚後一同居住在[[費城|費城]]。辛蒂本人也是大型啤酒公司[[安海斯-布希|安海斯-布希]]产品分销商Hansley公司的董事長，這個公司是由她父親創立的<ref>[http://www.abwholesaler.com/hensley/AboutUs/Contacts "About Us: Our People"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061020132601/http://www.abwholesaler.com/hensley/AboutUs/Contacts |date=2006-10-20 }}, Hensley & Company website, URL last accessed 2006-11-14.</ref><ref>[http://biz.yahoo.com/ic/121/121680.html "Hensley & Company company profile"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080112035148/http://biz.yahoo.com/ic/121/121680.html |date=2008-01-12 }}, Yahoo! Finance, URL last accessed 2006-11-14.</ref>。辛蒂在2004年4月時曾經因高血壓而中風，但目前顯然已經康復了<ref>{{cite news | title = Cindy McCain goes home; full recovery is expected |url=http://www.azcentral.com/specials/special39/articles/0417mccain17.html|date= 2004-04-17 |first = Judi |last = Villa |publisher = Arizona Central |accessdate = 2006-08-16 }}</ref>。

麥凱恩因戰爭的經歷，長年來曾接受多次醫療以治療身上的[[皮膚癌|皮膚癌]]和[[胎記瘤|胎記瘤]]，但病症仍一再復發，最近的幾次包括1993年、2000年、和2002年<ref name="#1"/>。2017年7月，麦凯恩接受手术切除右眼附近的一个血块，随后确诊患有[[脑瘤|脑瘤]]中常见的[[膠質母細胞瘤|膠質母細胞瘤]]<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2017/jul/19/john-mccain-brain-cancer|title=John McCain has been diagnosed with brain cancer, spokesman says|publisher=The Guardian|date=2017-07-20|accessdate=2017-07-20|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109024029/https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2017/jul/19/john-mccain-brain-cancer|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年8月24日，即麥凱恩逝世前一日，麥凱恩的家人發出聲明，指麥凱恩決定不繼續接受針對膠質母細胞瘤的治療<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/227146/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E9%BA%A5%E5%87%B1%E6%81%A9%E6%82%A3%E8%85%A6%E7%99%8C-%E6%90%8F%E9%AC%A5%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E5%A4%9A-%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E6%94%BE%E6%A3%84%E6%B2%BB%E7%99%82 |title=美國參議員麥凱恩患腦癌　搏鬥一年多　宣布放棄治療 |author=許懿安 |date=2018-08-25 |publisher=香港01 |language=zh-hk |accessdate=2018-08-25 |archive-date=2019-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190606134302/https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/227146/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E9%BA%A5%E5%87%B1%E6%81%A9%E6%82%A3%E8%85%A6%E7%99%8C-%E6%90%8F%E9%AC%A5%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E5%A4%9A-%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E6%94%BE%E6%A3%84%E6%B2%BB%E7%99%82 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

麥凱恩育有七名子女以及四名孫子女。麥凱恩收養了第一任妻子Carol Shepp和她前夫的兩名兒子道格(Doug)和安迪(Andy)，以及一名女兒西妮(Sidney)。麥凱恩與第二任妻子辛蒂生下了三名子女—就讀於[[哥倫比亞大學|哥倫比亞大學]]（2007）的梅根(Meghan)、就讀於[[美国海军学院|美国海军学院]]（2009）的傑克(Jack)、以及就讀於{{link-en|布羅菲大學預備學校|Brophy College Preparatory}}的詹姆斯(Jimmy)。除此之外，他與辛蒂多年前曾從一間位於[[孟加拉國|孟加拉]]由[[德蕾莎修女|德蕾莎修女]]經營的孤兒院中認養了一名小女兒布麗姬特(Bridget)。麥凱恩的兒子詹姆士在2006年被[[美国海军陆战队|海军陆战队]]徵召入伍，並且在2006年9月開始新兵訓練<ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.marinecorpstimes.com/story.php?f=1-292925-1990039.php |title= Sen. McCain-{’}-s youngest son joins Marine Corps |work= Marine Corps Times |publisher= Associated Press
|date= 2006-07-31 |accessdate= 2006-08-01 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20060801192307/http://www.marinecorpstimes.com/story.php?f=1-292925-1990039.php |archivedate= 2006年8月1日}}</ref>，於2008年初結束第一次派赴伊拉克戰場任務。

